otherFacts.name: InteriorFeatures
otherFacts.value: Separate Shower, Garden Tub, Entrance Foyer

data.description: You will FALL IN LOVE with this beautiful ranch style home with open concept that features a large open living room w/vaulted ceilings and brick fireplace. Open Kitchen with granite countertops, tons of cabinet space, breakfast bar and breakfast area. Large master bedroom on the main with walk-in closet. Master bath with separate shower and garden tub. Two spacious secondary bedrooms on the main with full bath. Upstairs you will fine an additional bedroom/bonus room. Rocking chair front porch. The backyard has a covered back porch perfect for a BBQ. This home sits on one of the largest lots in the neighborhood and also sits on a corner lot in a cul de sac. Located in the sought after Kimbell Farm Estates subdivision.   ***PROFESSIONAL INTERIOR PICTURES WILL BE AVAILABLE TUESDAY*** You can come inside and see for yourself before the pictures. This home will go fast!
